        "created_at": "2018-05-13T18:24:25.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Dale\u2013find some 2011.  Makes one wish for bad summer weather or at least a major cooling trend.  Best year for a number of washington wineries with savvy winemakers.  Not sure if Ben would sell you any of what he has, but it must be available out there somewhere.</p>",
