        "created_at": "2018-05-13T20:55:40.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"john stimson\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n john stimson:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Dale\u2013find some 2011.  Makes one wish for bad summer weather or at least a major cooling trend.  Best year for a number of washington wineries with savvy winemakers.  Not sure if Ben would sell you any of what he has, but it must be available out there somewhere.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Warmly seconded. Great for Betz, Andrew Will, Cayuse and plenty of others. But you had to be diligent and work hard.</p>",
